00:26:11.278 --> 00:26:12.571
<i>Paul said…</i>

443
00:26:12.654 --> 00:26:15.532
<i>♪ You are far ♪</i>

444
00:26:16.032 --> 00:26:19.244
<i>♪ Far as the sky ♪</i>

445
00:26:19.327 --> 00:26:25.333
<i>♪ You are always on my mind ♪</i>

446
00:26:25.834 --> 00:26:29.296
<i>♪ You are far. baby ♪</i>

447
00:26:29.379 --> 00:26:32.757
<i>♪ Far away ♪</i>

