00:31:35.518 --> 00:31:36.394
<i>[music fades]</i>

539
00:31:37.562 --> 00:31:38.646
<i>Babes.</i>

540
00:31:38.730 --> 00:31:39.564
<i>Hey.</i>

541
00:31:40.356 --> 00:31:41.316
<i>Sorry I'm late.</i>

