<i>Meet me how?</i>

548
00:31:58.666 --> 00:32:02.587
<i>I didn't know</i>
<i>you were Prophet Josiah Obalolu's son.</i>

549
00:32:04.797 --> 00:32:05.632
<i>So?</i>

