572
00:33:22.083 --> 00:33:23.209
<i>[chuckles]</i>

573
00:33:24.043 --> 00:33:26.546
<i>-Reks!</i>
<i>-Come. let me show. come! Come!</i>

574
00:33:28.297 --> 00:33:30.299
<i>[in Pidgin] Look at it! Look at it!</i>

575
00:33:31.384 --> 00:33:32.677
