00:33:38.516 --> 00:33:39.350
<i>Reks!</i>

579
00:33:39.434 --> 00:33:41.060
<i>[in Pidgin] Yes. it's me.</i>

580
00:33:41.144 --> 00:33:43.438
<i>This house. I paid in cash.</i>

